article.headline: Aranguren scores 22 to lead Iona over Colgate 85-65

images.name: Jean Aranguren drills home 3-pointer and-1 for Iona
images.caption: Jean Aranguren drills home 3-pointer and-1 for Iona

article.linkText: Aranguren scores 22 to lead Iona over Colgate 85-65
article.story: NEW ROCHELLE, N.Y. -- — Jean Aranguren scored 22 points as Iona beat Colgate 85-65 on Thursday night. Aranguren added eight rebounds for the Gaels (5-7). Idan Tretout scored 14 points, shooting 5 for 11, including 2 for 5 from beyond the arc. Wheza Panzo had 12 points and shot 4 for 10, including 3 for 7 from beyond the arc. Braeden Smith led the way for the Raiders (6-6) with 14 points, five assists and two steals. Colgate also got 10 points from Sam Thomson. In addition, Ryan Moffatt finished with nine points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
